  "text": "Finally, we measure latency on real bird song aligned as in [CITATION_1] . This extracts and aligns the centres of the sampled songs, and the canonical signal is given with respect to that alignment. These timing measurements reflect not only detector performance, but also the variability of the bird's song.",
